<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="station-n">station <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'steɪʃn/    美 /'steɪʃn/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>车站：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the station platform
站台</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>train / railway station</strong>
火车站</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>go to the station to see sb off
到车站为某人送行</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>站；所；台；局：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a police / fire / TV / gas station
警察局/消防站/电视台/加油站</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the International Space Station
国际空间站</p></div></div>